gomodel:SYNGO_1583  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099059 replaced by GO:0048787" , "Rationale: An antibody against mGluR7a (G71) was used to localize mGluR7a in the rat hippocampus. Slices of rat brain were processed for immunogold EM and mGluR7a was found to localize to the presynape of perforant path CA1, CA3 and DG neurons and mossy fibers. Both symmetric and asymmetric synapses were observed\n\n20/11/2017 Pim\n- Based on the known transmembrane topology of the protein, the \"integral component of ... membrane\" term was chosen.. Experimental description: Wistar, materials & methods" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-5648-066X" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-2533-9548" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-4022-8707" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-7480-0826" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1212-5623" ;
